msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_11_kiev/date"
msgid "November 7th, 1943 · Fastov, Kyiv oblast"
msgstr "7 de noviembre de 1943 - Fastov, provincia de Kyiv"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_11_kiev/name"
msgid "Street to Street <c(a655af)>[DLC]</c>"
msgstr "De calle en calle <c(a655af)>[DLC]</c>"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_11_kiev/name_big"
msgid "Street to Street"
msgstr "De calle en calle"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_11_kiev/narrator/officer/01"
msgid ""
"Comrades, welcome to Fastov! The city is crawling with Fascists behind every "
"window, our job is to liberate the city by force!"
msgstr ""
"Camaradas, ¡bienvenidos a Fastov! La ciudad está llena de fascistas en cada "
"ventana, ¡nuestro trabajo es liberar la ciudad a base de fuerza bruta!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_11_kiev/narrator/officer/02"
msgid ""
"Show no mercy! Drive the invaders from our city, but be cautious at every "
"corner. The enemy is well prepared for our arrival."
msgstr ""
"¡No tengais piedad! ¡Expulsad a los invasores de nuestra ciudad! pero tened "
"cuidado en cada esquina. El enemigo está bien preparado para nuestra llegada."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_11_kiev/narrator/officer/03"
msgid ""
"The enemy has barricaded the streets. Some of those rubble piles are too "
"damn high to climb or to blow up. You will have to go around them to get to "
"the city centre!"
msgstr ""
"El enemigo ha puesto barricadas en las calles. Algunas de esas pilas de "
"escombros son demasiado altas para escalarlas o hacerlas explotar. Tendrás "
"que rodearlas para llegar al centro de la ciudad"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_11_kiev/narrator/officer/04"
msgid ""
"Reinforcements are at your disposal. Crush the enemy, Comrade. There is no "
"room for defeat."
msgstr ""
"Los refuerzos están a tu disposición. Aplasta al enemigo, camarada. No "
"podemos contemplar una derrota."

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_11_kiev/narrator/officer/05"
msgid "Tiger tank, coming from the east!"
msgstr "¡Tanque Tigre, viniendo del este!"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_11_kiev/narrator/officer/06"
msgid "Watch out! There's an anti-tank gun at the end of this street!"
msgstr "¡Cuidado! ¡Hay un cañón antitanque al final de esta calle!"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_11_kiev/narrator/officer/07"
msgid "Great work, Soldiers!"
msgstr "¡Gran trabajo, soldados!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_11_kiev/narrator/officer/08"
msgid "Enemy heavy tank destroyer spotted on the southeast!"
msgstr "¡Cañón autopropulsado pesado enemigo avistado en el sureste!"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_11_kiev/narrator/officer/09"
msgid "An enemy tank is approaching from the south!"
msgstr "¡Un tanque enemigo se acerca desde el sur!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_11_kiev/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Congratulations on a job well done! Your veterancy really showed in this "
"battle. It won’t be long until we reach the Polish border, and the "
"liberation of the entire Soviet Union is a matter of time. A favorable "
"report, describing how your actions led to victory, will be sent to HQ. "
"Great job!"
msgstr ""
"¡Felicidades por un trabajo bien realizado! Su veteranía realmente se mostró "
"útil en esta batalla. No falta mucho para llegar a la frontera polaca, y la "
"liberación de toda la Unión Soviética es solo cuestión de tiempo. Se enviará "
"al cuartel general un informe favorable, describiendo cómo tus acciones "
"condujeron a la victoria. "

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_11_kiev/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"That is rather unexpected to say the least! Did you really just allow these "
"exhausted and starving Germans to mess up your attack? We need more resolve "
"and aggression for the next attempt. You should try a different approach. Go "
"back out there and try again."
msgstr ""
"¡Esto es bastante inesperado! ¿Realmente has permitido que estos alemanes "
"exhaustos y hambrientos arruinaran tu ataque? Necesitamos más determinación "
"y agresividad para el próximo intento. Deberías intentar un enfoque "
"diferente. Vuelve a salir y prueba de nuevo."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1943_11_kiev/place"
msgid "3rd Guards Tank Army (1st Ukranian Front)"
msgstr "3er Ejército de Tanques de la Guardia (1er Frente Ucraniano)"

